snippet.title: Lagaf: Les Aventures de Moktar - Vol 1: La Zoubida (PC DOS) - Playthrough Level 1
snippet.description:
Les Aventures de Moktar by Titus (1991)
PC DOS version, playing in DOSBox 0.74. Completing Level 1 showing all secrets and get the ball.
In 1992 new version of this game was released in English under the title - Titus the Fox, with a different main character...

More info and download:
http://www.oldgames.sk/en/game/lagaf-les-aventures-de-moktar/
